{"tid":829124,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"【日經】搬左出去住嘅巴絲，你地比幾錢老豆老母？","createTime":"2018-09-20T07:52:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-20T09:02:09.000Z","uid":169207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d05d13b16de5d2e3c68fa8149a9a2d8331d48e9d","tid":829124,"uid":169207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T07:52:34.000Z","msg":"一直同老豆老母關係都ok<br />\n不過次撚次講親家用就鬧交<br />\n因為我呀哥比50% 老母話咁先係孝順<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n問題黎啦<br />\n遲啲會同男朋友搬出去住<br />\n老母話要照比家用，仲要同宜家一樣咁多<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁邊度仲有錢剩<br />\n佢話「咁唔好搬出去住」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果唔比家用就唔使旨意佢第時會幫我任何野<br />\n（雖然我都唔知佢可以幫到我啲咩）<br />\n宜家住緊層樓係呀哥名，咁佢比50%都好正常<br />\n但我乜撚野都無，老豆老母都夠錢用<br />\n點解唔放過我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n唔計講起家用，其實我同老豆老母都好fd<br />\n我唔想傷感情<br />\n但宜家擺明勒索，可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf8a0ddc04be084b04bbb2aacc0ba1cb6f28fbfb","tid":829124,"uid":98601,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T07:56:28.000Z","msg":"50%，比嗰個都on9"},{"pid":"b44c4a96f4eca046c05d5e2d804a5293c5e8bc40","tid":829124,"uid":68902,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T07:59:35.000Z","msg":"用金錢衡量嘅家人，要嚟把L？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":